clock-description =
    A clean, configurable clock widget for the FreeSynergy desktop.

    Displays the current time in analog or digital format. Supports 12-hour
    and 24-hour digital modes, a configurable time zone, and adapts its colors
    to the active desktop theme.

clock-features =
    - Analog, 12-hour digital, and 24-hour digital display modes
    - Configurable time zone
    - Adapts to the active desktop theme
    - Compact — fits in 2x1 grid slots
